sources.title: San Francisco (1960) Michael Landon, Lorne Greene | Classic Western
sources.description:
The Cartwrights finish a cattle drive in San Francisco with Hop Sing. Ben is shanghaied at the Barbary Coast while searching for a pair of ranch hands. With guest stars; Kathleen Crowley, Richard Deacon, James Hong, and David White.
 
Director: Arthur Lubin
Writer: Thomas Thompson
Stars: Michael Landon, Lorne Greene, Pernell Roberts
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western, Bonanza

metadata.Plot: Lidia,the daughter of a family in an Italian port town becomes pregnant. Her cousin Tina is jealous when Lidia then turns to another man, her own lover.
metadata.Writer: Jean Aurenche, Pierre Bost, Pier Antonio Quarantotti Gambini
